{"tid":1540370,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"(ENGLISH) Breaking news: Carrie Lam PROPOSES to withdraw","createTime":"2019-09-04T11:21:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T12:20:41.000Z","uid":128348,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"85fbb64fc0314d39bb45621aad4fa1093250509c","tid":1540370,"uid":128348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:21:44.000Z","msg":"‪The HK government hasnt withdraw the bill. <br />\nThey only propose to but it still has not been confirmed. <br />\n<br />\nThe announcement is relieve the tension before the Human Rights and Democracy act discussion. <br />\n<br />\nThe US PARLIAMENT's discussion on the Human Rights and Democracy Bill will threaten the community interest, Carrie Lam and the communist supporters are afraid that their wealth may get frozen or imposed to sanctions."},{"pid":"f9460d67ae0fdfa3237813fa77d1bc44320ed88b","tid":1540370,"uid":128348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:23:33.000Z","msg":"SELF PUSH"},{"pid":"2dd956ccf84c8e93951588e4d92440c407f5fdb3","tid":1540370,"uid":128348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:23:43.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"4063d4b186430da11ab175ccf3bb25a17a30bfa3","tid":1540370,"uid":247845,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:23:44.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Our friends that we've lost would not forgive us if we accepted those from the government</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a96f59080dd7bfb477e88685f489275506ee5db3","tid":1540370,"uid":128348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:24:01.000Z","msg":"Lihkg Carrie Lam news"},{"pid":"cade99c24d7519fa200cbe627c3bca545dc33935","tid":1540370,"uid":263822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,